<div class='single-wrap'>
    <article id="post-1497758" class="single article post-1497758 post type-post status-publish format-image has-post-thumbnail category-world tag-florida tag-florida-school-shooting tag-parkland-school-shooting tag-watch post_format-post-format-image channel-theblaze-news" data-feed-type="story">

                
        <header class="article-header">
            <h1 class="page-title">Parkland students lash out at Trump, NRA on Sunday talk shows: &#8216;You sicken me&#8217;</h1>            <div class="article-header-inner">
            <span class="article-dates">
        <time class="entry-date feed-time published" datetime="2018-02-18T21:26:23-05:00">Feb 18, 2018 9:26 pm</time>
          </span>
</div>

        </header>

        <div class="article-image ">
                <figure><img width="1280" height="720" src="/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-1280x720.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Parkland students lash out at Trump, NRA on Sunday talk shows: &#8216;You sicken me&#8217;" srcset="https://www.theblaze.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://www.theblaze.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-768x432.jpg 768w, https://www.theblaze.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-384x216.jpg 384w, https://www.theblaze.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-192x108.jpg 192w, https://www.theblaze.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-96x54.jpg 96w, https://www.theblaze.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/parklandstudentsnratrumpinaction-100x55.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></figure>

        <figcaption>Students who attend the the Parkland, Florida, high school targeted by a shooter last week demand action from President Donald Trump and politicians. (Image source: YouTube screenshot) </figcaption>
        </div>

        <aside class="article-misc ">
